strings.Value: {n}Stretching lusciously, Octavia gathers her clothes from their scattered places on the floor and gets dressed.{/n} "Mmm... I love you. Let's do this more often!"
{n}Octavia clings to you, kissing you passionately and tenderly biting your lips.{/n}
{n}Octavia presses her finger to your lips.{/n} "Shh... Don't say this, or our love might be shorter than I'd like."
"But I only got dressed..." {n}The half-elf undoes one button on her shirt and smiles flirtatiously.{/n} "Now you'll have to help me take it all off again..."

"While I was a slave, I used to dream of freedom. Now sometimes in my dreams I wake up in a cage, and meeting you and all our adventures is just a dream. Dreams are such strange things... But I feel for some reason that these nightmares won't be coming back. What's happened now... It's too real to confuse with a dream."
